{"tid":1082897,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"據了解王志民提及選舉　稱中國人不用「成功爭取」字眼","createTime":"2019-03-29T08:49:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-29T09:50:18.000Z","uid":98777,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e801b106f694751ddda1839dccdd5a0060bb6ba8","tid":1082897,"uid":98777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T08:49:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1450365-20190329.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1450365-20190329.htm&d=88BycQanWGa6BXzVat85HVR4K0ufT%2FFGu3kbIPb6xA8%3D&h=5a897a42\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1450365-20190329.htm&h=25af4d05\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1450365-20190329.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n特區政府邀請全國人大代表兼中聯辦主任王志民出席宣講會，向全體問責官員、首長級官員，行政會議成員等，宣講兩會精神。<br />\n<br />\n宣講會早上在政府總部舉行，據了解，財政司司長陳茂波及律政司司長鄭若驊都有向王志民提問。其中陳茂波問到，預料中美貿易展的發展如何，以及幾時會完結，王志民並無正面回應。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，王志民在會上用了很多較地道的例子解釋，例如他提及香港的選舉，有政黨會用「成功爭取」某些議題爭取支持，情況較接近外國的政治文化，但他說，中國人一向較為含蓄，即使成功做到一些事情，亦不會用類似字眼去表達。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n禮 義 廉？？？<br />\n<br />\n中國人包括香港人講咩都要俾人管，恭喜香港回祖國"},{"pid":"ce33633d8d28d30054fca7c01954472227eaa22e","tid":1082897,"uid":152476,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T08:51:32.000Z","msg":"因為權利唔可以係賤民爭取，係當權者賜予"},{"pid":"29d3a53409ac6f2808e1fed7545358b103010798","tid":1082897,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T08:51:40.000Z","msg":"同禮義廉割席?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e673f39016f9e088ae18f135e870058a1b5b2265","tid":1082897,"uid":44199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T09:33:11.000Z","msg":"即係講緊淫賤聯連支那閪都不如?"},{"pid":"0c46c8b93f8afb81f5f342a6a08a0ae39dcb2148","ti